Label: First page number
Description: The number of the first page of a sequence of contiguous pages. Mandatory in each occurrence of the <PageRun> composite, and non-repeating. Note that here and in the <LastPageNumber> element a page ‘number’ may be Arabic, Roman, or an alphanumeric string (eg L123).
Format: <dd>Variable length alphanumeric, suggested maximum length 20 characters</dd>
